Package: SMARTAGL
Title: Smart Above Ground Level Flight Path Planning
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Antonio", "Castaneda", 
           email = "antonio.castanedag@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides advanced terrain-aware flight path planning with two core methods:
    (1) True constant AGL height (SMARTAGL) and (2) Angled sensor terrain following. 
    Generates optimized paths for drone missions with digital elevation model integration,
    automatic coordinate transformation, and UgCS-compatible exports.
